	<p>I've been considering buying a horse for a while, but I haven't been able to find exactly what it does.  I understand that on a hrose you med as long as you aren't moving or fighting, but does fighting mean that you are in auto attack or does it mean that a mob is attacking you?  On a horse can you just stand there and get hit, and still get the horse med effect.  Second, do you med through spells on a horse?  For example, do you med through canna casts, med through JBB usage, both or neither?<br />
<br />
Thanks,<br />
Krac, 44 Troll Shaman, Zeb</p>
	
	
	
	
	
