	<!-- message -->
	<p>You med as long as you are not moving and dont have auto attack on.  So if you like to swing your weapon inbetween jbb casts you lose that.  <br />
<br />
Another benifit is you can swap spells out on the run.  That can be very usefull when you get suprised.  If you get hit spell book closes.  I also used to close my spell book by standing up.  This doesnt work so you have to click close or use escape to close it and lose your target.</p>
	
	
	
